             <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> Description:这是emlog的默认模板，简洁明快 ……<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
             <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> Author:emlog开发小组<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
             <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> Author Url:http://www.emlog.net<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
             <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> Sidebar Amount:1<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
             <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> */<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
             <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> if(!defined('EMLOG_ROOT')) {exit('error!');}<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
             <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> require_once (getViews('module'));<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
