           <span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin-left:43px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;color:#336699 !important;">复制代码</span> 
          </div> 这一段是导航栏，因此我们将php标签以及注释符去掉，接着将<span style="word-wrap:break-word;color:red;">&lt;?php _e('Home'); ?&gt;</span>替换成<span style="word-wrap:break-word;color:red;">Home</span>（注1），注意此处链接应为<span style="word-wrap:break-word;color:red;">./</span>而不是<span style="word-wrap:break-word;color:red;">/</span>，补上一个半角逗号<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> 下面有个WP的函数<span style="word-wrap:break-word;color:red;">&lt;?php wp_list_pages('title_li=&amp;depth=1&amp;sort_column=menu_order'); ?&gt;</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#000000;">，不管它，删了</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> 然后从默认模板中复制一下代码 
          <div class="blockcode" style="overflow:hidden;margin:10px 0px;padding:10px 0px 5px 10px;color:#666666;zoom:1;border:1px solid #CCCCCC;background:url(http://bbs.emlog.net/static/image/common/codebg.gif) 0px 0px repeat-y #F7F7F7;"> 
           <div id="code_CZ7"> 
            <ol style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 10px !important;padding:0px !important;"> 
