      <p> <span style="color:#444444;font-family:'Tahoma, Microsoft Yahei, Simsun';"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-weight:700;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;color:seagreen;">第五步：log_list.php</span></span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">先将</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">index.php</span><span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">重命名为</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">log_list.php</span><span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">，然后打开它</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">将第一行</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php get_header(); ?&gt;</span><span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">给替换成</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php if(!defined('EMLOG_ROOT')) {exit('error!');}?&gt;</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">考虑到本模板首页突出显示了第一片日志，因此先打开</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">home.php</span><span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">，复制如下代码</span> </span></span> </p> 
