      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">接着删掉</span>
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php the_post(); ?&gt;，</span>
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">继续往下看，同第五步，参考默认模板echo_log.php修改相应php代码，修改前后如下</span> 
      <div class="blockcode" style="overflow:hidden;margin:10px 0px;padding:10px 0px 5px 10px;color:#666666;zoom:1;border:1px solid #CCCCCC;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background:url(http://bbs.emlog.net/static/image/common/codebg.gif) 0px 0px repeat-y #F7F7F7;"> 
