      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">最后，将</span>
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php get_footer(); ?&gt;</span>
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">替换成</span>
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php include getViews('footer'); ?&gt;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">至此，</span>
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">echo_log.php</span>
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">修改完成</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">下面是</span>
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">page.php</span>
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">，复制一个</span>
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">echo_log.php</span>
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">，重命名为</span>
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">page.php</span>
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">（删掉原有的page.php）</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">打开它，删除如下代码即可：</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php echo date('Y-n-j G:i l', $date); ?&gt;&nbsp;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php editflg($logid,$author); ?&gt;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php blog_sort($sortid, $logid); ?&gt;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php doAction('log_related'); ?&gt;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php blog_tag($logid); ?&gt;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php blog_trackback(); ?&gt;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:red;">&lt;?php neighbor_log(); ?&gt;</span>
      <br style="word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;" /> 
      <span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">这些代码附近的一些相关的html也要删除，如本例中的</span> 
      <div class="blockcode" style="overflow:hidden;margin:10px 0px;padding:10px 0px 5px 10px;color:#666666;zoom:1;border:1px solid #CCCCCC;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background:url(http://bbs.emlog.net/static/image/common/codebg.gif) 0px 0px repeat-y #F7F7F7;"> 
       <div id="code_Mte"> 
        <ol style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 10px !important;padding:0px !important;"> 
         <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> <br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
         <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;div class=&quot;navigation&quot;&gt;<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
         <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;?php neighbor_log(); ?&gt;<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
         <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;<br style="word-wrap:break-word;" /> </li> 
         <li style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px 0px 0px 2em;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px;list-style-type:decimal-leading-zero;font-family:Monaco, Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Courier New', serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8em;"> </li> 
